## 7. Data Model

New fields added to the `clients` table in Supabase:

| Column | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `stripe_customer_id` | `text` | Stripe Customer ID (`cus_xxx`) |
| `stripe_subscription_id` | `text` | Active Stripe Subscription ID (`sub_xxx`) |
| `stripe_subscription_status` | `text` | Mirrors Stripe status: `active`, `past_due`, `canceled`, etc. |
| `stripe_price_id` | `text` | Currently active Stripe Price ID |
| `subscription_interval` | `text` | `monthly`, `quarterly`, `biannual`, `annual` |
| `current_period_end` | `timestamptz` | End of current billing period |

