## 8. Technical Architecture

```
Client Browser
     │
     ▼
Superwork Frontend (Next.js / React)
     │  Plan selection, billing dashboard, portal redirect
     │
     ▼
Superwork API (server-side)
     │  Creates Checkout Sessions, Customer Portal Sessions
     │  Validates webhook signatures
     │
     ▼
Stripe API
     │  Subscription lifecycle, card storage, invoicing
     │
     └──► Webhook ──► POST /api/stripe/webhook ──► Supabase DB
```

**Environment Variables Required:**

```
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
STRIPE_CUSTOMER_PORTAL_URL=https://billing.stripe.com/...
```

