## 12. Analytics & Reporting (Internal)

Tracked via Stripe Dashboard and optionally synced to internal analytics:

- MRR / ARR by plan
- Churn rate (cancellations per period)
- Failed payment rate
- Breakdown by billing interval (monthly vs. annual)
- Average revenue per client

