## 13. Phased Rollout

### Phase 1 — Core Billing (MVP)
- Stripe Checkout integration for new client subscriptions
- Monthly and annual intervals only
- Webhook handling for core events
- Billing dashboard with Stripe Customer Portal
- Access gating based on subscription status

### Phase 2 — Interval Expansion
- Add quarterly and bi-annual options
- Display savings badges on longer commitments

### Phase 3 — Enhanced Billing UX
- Embedded Stripe Elements (replace hosted Checkout for a seamless in-portal experience)
- Proration on mid-cycle plan changes
- Coupon/discount code entry at checkout
- VAT/tax collection via Stripe Tax

